{"tid":1363191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【IT友／連登Admin入】成立一個歷史恥辱柱　將香港罪人永久釘喺上面！","createTime":"2019-07-25T05:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T07:32:24.000Z","uid":14328,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"70b9efc190f71c0cee4ed44841e3080c23ec15ba","tid":1363191,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:55:47.000Z","msg":"建議架構一個網站，用類似WIKI嘅形式，比連登用戶寫返自己嘅香港歷史，如果唔係好多事，好快會被遺忘。用網路去將惡人的罪行釘係恥辱柱，等佢同子孫都遺臭萬年。更加要紀錄為香港民主犧牲嘅烈士，立一個網路版烈士紀念碑，令佢地永垂千古。<br />\n<br />\n此舉有莫大好處<br />\n<br />\n１）對當權者有小小阻嚇力，即使作惡後，亦令後人永記其惡行。<br />\n２）他朝香港人權與民主法案通過後，美國可以用嚟參考批唔批VISA／凍結資產<br />\n３）紀錄低烈士嘅遺志，周不時可以比連登仔進行網路參拜。<br />\n<br />\n小弟唔識寫網站，不過可以幫手寫歷史"},{"pid":"e1d55696062ee9baaa9fff5d5a70d51b6d7462f8","tid":1363191,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:56:43.000Z","msg":"lm開wiki"},{"pid":"cfe04ac300e0f1fe6e50609f9fbe16e40c488bb2","tid":1363191,"uid":271267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:58:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要釘埋啲仆街既後代</span></span>"},{"pid":"e36f1dd7d5317596571444901a457fa3bfca3c33","tid":1363191,"uid":14328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cfe04ac300e0f1fe6e50609f9fbe16e40c488bb2","tid":1363191,"uid":271267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:58:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要釘埋啲仆街既後代</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />特別係林鄭啲仔女<br />\n老母係香港反民主，搞白色恐怖<br />\n有咩理由仔女可以係英國ＨＡＰＰＹ？"},{"pid":"082cc1acb21c98918b02998128916c2374624a9b","tid":1363191,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d0e163389bd9060bd45691662a3a39f3ba6a8c","tid":1363191,"uid":14328,"like":0,"disli